### Test für RestaurantResource

### Alle Restaurants abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants
Accept: application/json

### Ein Restaurant nach ID abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/1
Accept: application/json

### Ein neues Restaurant erstellen
POST http://localhost:8080/restaurants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Best Restaurant",
  "address": "101 Food St",
  "description": "The best place for food.",
  "rating": 4.5
}

### Ein Restaurant aktualisieren
PUT http://localhost:8080/restaurants/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Best Restaurant Updated",
  "address": "101 Food St, Suite 100",
  "description": "Even better place for food.",
  "rating": 4.8
}

### Ein Restaurant löschen
DELETE http://localhost:8080/restaurants/1

### Alle Bewertungen eines Restaurants abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/1/reviews
Accept: application/json

### Restaurants nach Name durchsuchen
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/search?name=Best
Accept: application/json


